  "id": "Hackney-2024_0966",
  "decision_conditions": [
    "<p>The Development hereby permitted shall only be carried out and completed strictly in accordance with the submitted plans hereby approved and any subsequent approval of details.\r\n</p><p><br></p><p>\r\nREASON: To ensure that the development hereby permitted is carried out in full accordance with the plans hereby approved.\r\n</p>",
    "&lt;p&gt;The roof of the ground floor element of the building shall not be used as a terrace, balcony or similar amenity area.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;REASON: In the interests of neighbours amenity&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The development shall be carried out in accordance with the details of the physical samples of materials for external surfaces particularly the copper cladding and the&amp;nbsp; 1:20 elevation details and 1:5 section of the windows as approved under application reference 2020/3728 unless otherwise superseded as part of the drawings hereby approved or agreed in writing by the Local Planning Authority.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;REASON: In order to ensure a satisfactory appearance for the proposed development, to safeguard the visual amenity of neighbouring properties and the appearance of the locality consistent with Policies D1, D3, D4 &amp;amp; HC1 of the London Plan 2021 &amp;amp; Policies LP1, LP2, LP3 &amp;amp; LP17 of the Hackney Local Plan 2020.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The development hereby permitted must be completed not later than the expiration of four months beginning with the date of this permission.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;REASON: In order to comply with the provisions of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990 (as amended).&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The development shall be carried out in accordance with the details of the cycle parking plan as approved under application reference&amp;nbsp;2020/3728&amp;nbsp;unless otherwise superseded as part of the drawings hereby approved or agreed in writing by the Local Planning Authority.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;REASON: To ensure that adequate provision for the safe and secure storage of bicycles is made for future occupiers and in the interest of improving highway conditions in general consistent with Policies T5 of the London Plan 2021 &amp;amp; Policies LP42 of the Hackney Local Plan 2020.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
  ],
